{"title":"黑的刷不成白","authors":["池北偶","方成"],"dates":[{"year":1982,"month":7,"day":1}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"黑的刷不成白"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"池北偶诗　方　成画"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白的抹不了黑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黑的刷不成白。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"放火并非点灯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"杀人不是彩排。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“皇军‘进入’支那”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“刺刀‘提携’脑袋”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"此等海外奇谈，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听来使人愤慨。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"侵略就是侵略，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"遮盖无法遮盖。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"芦沟桥的弹痕，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"石头城的血债，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"细菌战的武器，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万人坑的尸骸……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"罪证大大的有，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"历史岂能涂改。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"教训应当记取，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"切莫愚弄后代。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"军国主义余孽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"休要再怀鬼胎。（附图片）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":7,"page_end":7}